➜湖北诗人朱翠荣（清美玉洁）：乌云
http://www.sohu.com/a/416485263_100115135	39522
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200904/1a9b68b02f224ea9813a1438caee2ecc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>乌云</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/朱翠荣(武汉)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">谁的手在倾倒墨水？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">乌紫，污渍，凭空横着涂抹</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">青肿云，天空不见白</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>围拢堆积的乌云垂下来</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>砸中眼眶，青肿痛</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>秋风为什么要吹大雨和悲凉</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">置入体内的夏日强光</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一次次启动抵抗</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">阴影渐瘦，心室止于肥大</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>写于2020年9月4日中午</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200904/39fd17def4e3421fa4b1059cd757bec8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
