➜浙江诗人虞崇庄：瑞安国旗教育舘随想（外一首）
http://www.sohu.com/a/416486794_100115135	40126
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200904/cd0af428a34a40fc97bdba069c9bfd25.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>瑞安国旗教育舘随想</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/虞崇庄</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">祖国山河一片红，五星闪耀照苍穹。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">战争洗礼光荣史，鲜血凝成卓越功。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">西岘舘藏怀烈士，外滩塑像赞曾公。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">抚今追昔心澎湃，华夏春回气象雄。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> <strong>曾公：国旗设计者瑞安人曾联松</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200904/98a966ca96b24e3eb36a675fc02c3c9d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> <strong> 曲 院 风 荷</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/虞崇庄</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">朱栏曲院枕荷塘，风送芙蕖满路香。</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
