➜湖北诗人木子：碎碎念
http://www.sohu.com/a/416487589_100115135	40303
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200904/479f1b231ea94b3d8c9ec974d3cf8508.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>碎碎念</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/木子</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不奢望岁月静好</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人生不会风平浪静</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不奢望荣华富贵</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">没有人一辈子顺风顺水</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">脚下的路</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">弯弯曲曲</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">坎坎坷坷</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我不知道用什么去丈量</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人生的高度</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只看到：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">春事远了 </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">炎夏过了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">雪色近了 </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">眼前 </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">便是这样一个摇晃的秋</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>花入梦</strong></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
